<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>YIP-26</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/feather-icons"></script>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
      }
      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      h4 {
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="m-0 p-0">
    <nav
      class="fixed top-0 z-50 flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-transparent shadow w-full"
    >
      <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->

    <section id="home" class="hero">
      <div class="hero__bg" role="img" aria-label="YIP background image"></div>
      <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="hero__content">
        <h1 class="hero_title">Young Innovators Program</h1>
        <h2 class="hero_subtitle">7th Edition</h2>
        <div class="hero__cta">
          <a class="btn btn--light" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
            >Rule Book</a
          >
          <a
            class="btn btn--solid"
            href="/register"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Register</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="about_container">
        <div class="about_grid">
          <div class="about_content">
            <p class="section_subheader">About Us</p>
            <h3 class="section_header">Event History</h3>
            <p class="para">
              The Young Innovators Program serves as a distinguished platform
              dedicated to fostering the scientific curiosity and
              problem-solving acumen of aspiring young minds.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p class="para">
              <strong>Eligibility Criteria:</strong>
              This competition exclusively welcomes students currently enrolled
              in grades VIII to XII, with the explicit objective of
              acknowledging and nurturing their creative potential. We implore
              you not to allow your exceptional ideas to languish in dormancy.
            </p>
            <br />
            <p class="para">
              Top teams nationwide will be selected after the first round and
              they will be called to Indian Institute of Technology, Kharagpur
              to exhibit and demonstrate their models or prototype and charts
              which will be evaluated by professors of IIT Kharagpur.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about_list">
            <div class="about_item" data-sr-id="5">
              <span>
                <i class="ri-global-fill"> </i>
              </span>
              <h4>Present projects to esteemed researchers and guests.</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="about_item" data-sr-id="6">
              <span>
                <i class="ri-bar-chart-fill"> </i>
              </span>
              <h4>Immerse in IIT Kharagpur's scientific environment.</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="about_item" data-sr-id="7">
              <span>
                <i class="ri-thumb-up-fill"> </i>
              </span>
              <h4>Join YIP'25 and shine.</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="timeline" class="section section--darkimage">
      <div class="section-bg" role="img" aria-label="Timeline background"></div>
      <div class="section-dim"></div>

      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section__title">Event Timeline</h2>
        <div class="section__line"></div>

        <div class="timeline">
          <article class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="tl-content">
              <h3 class="tl-title">Registration</h3>
              <p>
                The principal needs to nominate a coordinating teacher for this
                program, who will be given a user ID and password for
                registration of the students. The students need to form a team
                of 2-3 members and submit their name and details to the
                coordinating teacher of the school.
              </p>
              <span class="tl-chip">Started </span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="tl-content">
              <h3 class="tl-title">Round 1</h3>
              <p>
                Round I Submission Starts The team will submit their abstract of
                the project ideas briefing the scientific proposal based on the
                chosen theme. The online submissions of the projects will be
                done by the coordinating teacher by using his/her user id and
                password on the portal. Round 1 results will be released on our
                website. All participants who make it to the next round will
                also receive the news via email. The selected students will
                proceed to round 2.
              </p>
              <span class="tl-chip">27th Oct - 15th Dec 2025</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="tl-content">
              <h3 class="tl-title">Round 2 (Semifinal) @ IIT Kharagpur</h3>
              <p>
                Top teams nationwide will be selected after the first round and
                they will be called to Indian Institute of Technology, Kharagpur
                to exhibit and demonstrate their models or prototype and charts
                which will be evaluated by professors of IIT Kharagpur. The
                selected team need to confirm their presence for a two-day event
                held at IIT Kharagpur. The registration fees for this round will
                be declared after the announcement of the results of the 1st
                round.Selected teams exhibit and demonstrate prototypes at IIT
                Kharagpur.
              </p>
              <span class="tl-chip">11th Jan 2025 </span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="tl-item">
            <div class="tl-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="tl-content">
              <h3 class="tl-title">Round 3 (Final) @ IIT Kharagpur</h3>
              <p>
                The qualifying teams from the second round will be qualified for
                the winners round. In this round each team will be given an
                opportunity to demonstrate their ideas in the form of a
                presentation followed by a Q&A session.
              </p>
              <span class="tl-chip">12th Jan 2025 </span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Gallery -->
    <section class="py-12 w-[100vw] h-screen" id="gallery">
      <h1 class="text-center my-6 font-[Montserrat] text-3xl font-semibold">
        Gallery
      </h1>

      <div
        class="relative bg-yellow-900 md:w-[700px] md:h-[400px] w-[75%] h-[75%] mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-lg"
        id="slider"
      >
        <!-- Slides -->
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide active"
        >
          <img
            src="images/gallery_1.jpg"
            alt="Gallery 1"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide"
        >
          <img
            src="images/gallery_2.jpg"
            alt="Gallery 2"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-1000 ease-in-out slide"
        >
          <img
            src="images/gallery_3.jpg"
            alt="Gallery 3"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Buttons -->
        <button
          class="absolute top-1/2 left-4 -translate-y-1/2 bg-black/50 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-black/70 transition z-10"
          onclick="changeSlide(-1)"
        >
          ⟨
        </button>
        <button
          class="absolute top-1/2 right-4 -translate-y-1/2 bg-black/50 text-white px-3 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-black/70 transition z-10"
          onclick="changeSlide(1)"
        >
          ⟩
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="py-16" id="testimonials">
      <h2 id="testimonial" class="text-center text-3xl font-bold mb-8">
        Testimonials
      </h2>
      <div class="w-4/5 mx-auto overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex transition-transform duration-500" id="sliderTrack">
          <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 text-center px-4">
            <img
              src="images/ShamrockInternationalSchool.jpg"
              class="w-[470px] h-[300px] mx-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
              Shamrock International School (YIP 2023)
            </h3>
            <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-sm mt-2">
              We thank the entire team of SBRC for the initiative...
            </p>
            <p class="italic mt-3">- Mrs AK Sindhu</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 text-center px-4">
            <img
              src="images/NHGoelSchool.jpeg.jpg"
              class="w-[470px] h-[300px] mx-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">NH GOEL SCHOOL (YIP 2023)</h3>
            <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-sm mt-2">
              Big thanks to Team SBRC for hosting such a great event...
            </p>
            <p class="italic mt-3">- Mrs AK Sindhu</p>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 text-center px-4">
            <img
              src="images/AtomicEnergyCentralSchool.jpg"
              class="w-[470px] h-[300px] mx-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
            />
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
              Atomic Energy Central School (YIP 2023)
            </h3>
            <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-sm mt-2">
              Thank you so much for all the help extended to us...
            </p>
            <p class="italic mt-3">- Mrs AK Sindhu</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Query -->
    <section
      class="bg-black/60 bg-cover bg-center py-16 text-white flex justify-center"
    >
      <div class="w-full max-w-lg p-6 rounded-lg">
        <span
          class="block w-28 mx-auto text-center bg-teal-600 py-2 rounded text-sm font-semibold mb-4"
          >Query</span
        >
        <h1 class="text-center text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">
          Have any doubts?
        </h1>
        <form class="space-y-4">
          <input
            type="text"
            placeholder="Name"
            class="w-full p-3 rounded-md text-black"
            required
          />
          <div class="flex gap-3 flex-col sm:flex-row w-full">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="Email"
              class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-3 rounded-md text-black"
              required
            />
            <input
              type="tel"
              placeholder="Phone No."
              class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-3 rounded-md text-black"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <textarea
            rows="4"
            placeholder="Enter your query..."
            class="w-full p-3 rounded-md text-black"
            required
          ></textarea>
          <button
            type="submit"
            class="block mx-auto w-1/3 py-3 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 rounded-md"
          >
            Send Query
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="bg-gray-950 text-center text-gray-400">
      <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </footer>

    <script src="JS/home.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
